import React from 'react' import './conso.css'; function ConsoComponent(props) { const [currentSlide,setCurrentSlide]=useState(0); const handleCheck=(path)=>{ const ad=new Audio(path); ad.play(); } const handleLeftClick=()=>{ const newSlide=currentSlide-1; setCurrentSlide(newSlide); props.onClick(newSlide); } const handleRightClick=()=>{ const newSlide=currentSlide+1; setCurrentSlide(newSlide); props.onClick(newSlide); } return (
) } export default ConsoComponent
